== What does it do? ==
When "Always show long date in status bar" is on the status bar will show the day of the month, month and year all the time.<br>
"Always show long date in status bar: On"<br>
[[File:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/LongDateInStatusBar.png|Status bar with long date]]<br><br>
When "Always show long date in status bar" is off, the status bar will show just the month and year.  The day of the month can be displayed by pausing the game.
"Always show long date in status bar: Off"<br>
[[File:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/ShortDateInStatusBar.png|Normal status bar]]<br>
== How do you use it? ==
Turn it on or off in the Configure Patches, Interface Tab.
